  "title": "XL Touch Up Glue Pen | Precision Wig Glue for Lace & Poly Systems, Waterproof, Sweat & Oil Resistant for All-Day Hold | 3 ml",
  "body_html": "<div><div id=\"productDescription\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-small\">\n <p><span>Ghostbond XL Glue Pen delivers a long-lasting, invisible hold for lace and poly wigs, withstanding sweat, humidity, and high temperatures.</span></p>\n</div></div><div><div id=\"feature-bullets\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-medium a-spacing-top-small\">\n <ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\">\n  <li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\"> STRONG HOLD IN ANY CLIMATE \u2013 DESIGNED FOR HIGH HUMIDITY AND OILY SCALPS GHOSTBOND XL Signature Glue Pen delivers unrivaled adhesive strength in even the toughest conditions. This precision pen provides an invisible, ultra-strong bond that\u2019s specially crafted for lace wigs and poly systems, making it the ultimate choice for those with oily scalps, or those frequently in hot, humid environments. Whether you\u2019re working out, facing high humidity, or exposed to high temperatures, GHOSTBOND XL provides a firm hold for a flawless look all day long. </span></li>\n  <li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\"> WATERPROOF AND TEMPERATURE-RESISTANT FORMULA FOR RELIABLE WEAR This adhesive is formulated to withstand sweat, moisture, and temperature fluctuations, keeping your hairpiece securely in place. GHOSTBOND XL ensures your lace wig or poly system remains undetectable and natural-looking, no matter the environment or activity level. Experience a secure hold that can endure intense physical activities or challenging weather conditions without losing adhesion. </span></li>\n  <li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\"> SKIN-SAFE, NON-REFLECTIVE BOND FOR A NATURAL FINISH GHOSTBOND XL is free of harsh chemicals and is dermatologist-tested to be gentle on sensitive skin. Its non-reflective formula absorbs light, eliminating shine and helping your wig blend seamlessly along the hairline. This innovative design ensures your wig looks natural and stays invisible, without the need for touch-ups throughout the day. </span></li>\n  <li class=\"a-spacing-mini\"><span class=\"a-list-item\"> ECO-FRIENDLY PACKAGING AND SUSTAINABLE INGREDIENTS In our commitment to a sustainable future, GHOSTBOND XL comes in eco-friendly, biodegradable packaging and uses ingredients that are safe for both you and the environment. Our adhesive aligns with Pro Hair Labs\u2019 commitment to quality, safety, and environmental consciousness, making it a responsible choice for both you and the planet. </span></li>\n </ul>\n <div data-csa-c-content-id=\"voyager-product-details-jumplink\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"voyager-product-details-jumplink\" data-csa-c-type=\"link\" class=\"a-section aok-hidden\">\n<span class=\"caretnext\">\u203a</span> <a id=\"seeMoreDetailsLink\" class=\"a-link-normal\" href=\"#productDetails\"> See more product details </a>\n </div>\n</div></div><div><div class=\"a-section a-spacing-small a-spacing-top-small\">\n <table class=\"a-normal a-spacing-micro\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr class=\"a-spacing-small po-color\">\n    <td class=\"a-span3\"><span class=\"a-size-base a-text-bold\">Color</span></td>\n    <td class=\"a-span9\"><span class=\"a-size-base po-break-word\">White</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr class=\"a-spacing-small po-container.type\">\n    <td class=\"a-span3\"><span class=\"a-size-base a-text-bold\">Package Information</span></td>\n    <td class=\"a-span9\"><span class=\"a-size-base po-break-word\">Bottle</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr class=\"a-spacing-small po-product_benefit\">\n    <td class=\"a-span3\"><span class=\"a-size-base a-text-bold\">Product Benefits</span></td>\n    <td class=\"a-span9\"><span class=\"a-size-base po-break-word\">Strong Hold in Any Climate</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr class=\"a-spacing-small po-brand\">\n    <td class=\"a-span3\"><span class=\"a-size-base a-text-bold\">Brand</span></td>\n    <td class=\"a-span9\"><span class=\"a-size-base po-break-word\">GHOSTBOND</span></td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr class=\"a-spacing